700329f-a.title: Bronx: 215th Street (East) - White Plains Road
700329f-a.text:
East 215th Street, at, and adjoining the S.E. corner of White Plains Road. The 1-story brick structure, at the corner, bears No. 3650 on the latter, and the 3-story frame houseC No. 706 East 215th Street. An inscription on the frame house reads: Columbia Music
Hall - 1888.
May 25, 1928.
P. L. Sperr.
